    "body": "Thanks for filing this issue.\n\nTo increase the speed of the custom module, please try adding `shell = [\"sh\", \"--noprofile\", \"--noprofile\"]` to the custom module definition to avoid running it in a fish shell and set `when` to `true` (without quotes).\n\nI have also opened an issue in the `starship-jj` repo with further suggestions on improving the speed of the custom module ([lanastara_foss/starship-jj#6](https://gitlab.com/lanastara_foss/starship-jj/-/issues/6)).",
